---
title: "Dynamic: Review New Applications"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin as Organization Admin
    participant UI as UI Components
    participant DataSvc as AccessIntelligenceDataService
    participant PersistSvc as ReportPersistenceService
    participant TaskSvc as SecurityTasksService
    participant AdminTaskSvc as AdminTaskService [Vault Team]
    participant TaskApiSvc as SecurityTasksApiService
    participant Server as Bitwarden Server

    Admin->>UI: opens Review New Applications
    UI->>DataSvc: report$ (subscribe)
    DataSvc-->>UI: AccessReportView
    UI->>UI: display report.getNewApplications()
    Note over UI: Shows apps where reviewedDate === null

    Admin->>UI: selects critical apps, submits review

    UI->>DataSvc: markApplicationsAsCritical$(selectedNames)
    DataSvc->>DataSvc: report.markApplicationAsCritical(name) × selected
    Note over DataSvc: View model mutation + recomputeSummary()

    UI->>DataSvc: markApplicationsAsReviewed$(allNames)
    DataSvc->>DataSvc: report.markApplicationAsReviewed(name, today) × all
    Note over DataSvc: View model mutation — no summary change

    DataSvc-->>UI: report$ emits (updated flags + review dates)

    DataSvc->>PersistSvc: saveApplicationMetadata$(report)
    PersistSvc->>Server: updateRiskInsightsApplicationData$() — critical flags + review dates

    DataSvc->>TaskSvc: requestPasswordChangeForCriticalApplications$(orgId, cipherIds)
    Note over TaskSvc: Derives cipher IDs for critical at-risk apps<br/>from report$ via AccessIntelligenceDataService
    TaskSvc->>AdminTaskSvc: bulkCreateTasks(orgId, tasks)
    Note over AdminTaskSvc: Creates security tasks for affected members<br/>(Vault Team service)
    AdminTaskSvc-->>TaskSvc: SecurityTask[]

    TaskSvc->>TaskApiSvc: loadTasks$(orgId)
    TaskApiSvc->>Server: getAllTasks(orgId)
    Server-->>TaskApiSvc: SecurityTask[]
    TaskApiSvc-->>TaskSvc: SecurityTask[]
    TaskSvc-->>UI: tasks$ emits updated task list
